                <p>Activities in NCC are categorized as under:-</p><br>

                <p>(a) Institutional Training</p><br>

                <p>(b) Camp Training</p><br>

                <p>(c) Attachment Training (Service Unit)</p><br>

                <p>(d) Air wing Training</p><br>

                <p>(e) Naval wing Training</p><br>

                <p>(f) Social Service and Community Development Activities.</p><br>

                <p>(g) Youth Exchange Program</p><br>

                <p>(h) Conduct of Republic Day Camp</p><br>

                <p>(i) Conduct of course at OTA Kamptee and OTA Gwalior for ANO’s.</p><br>

                <p>(j) Career Counselling and Personality Development.</p><br>

                <p>(k) Remount & Veterinary Unit Training.</p><br>

                <p>(l) Conduct of Certificate Examinations.</p><br>

                <p>(m) Conduct of Adventure Activities. </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
              <a class="collapsed card-link darkcolor" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse44">44. Can I get any award for some extraordinary work/performance? </a>
