                <p>Merit and extraordinary work/performance is duly recognized at every level (at the Sub-Unit/ Unit/ Group/ Directorate/ HQ DGNCC levels) and is adequately rewarded/awarded in the NCC. For details contact you’re OC/CO Unit. </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
              <a class="collapsed card-link darkcolor" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse45">45. Can I get any chance for visiting other States in the country or abroad? How? </a>
            </div>
            <div id="collapse45" class="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">
              <div class="card-body">
                <p>Yes. If you are selected for Centrally Organised Camps/ Youth Exchange Programme. </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
              <a class="collapsed card-link darkcolor" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse46">46. How will NCC be useful in developing my personality? </a>
            </div>
            <div id="collapse46" class="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">
              <div class="card-body">
                <p>Please see the Aims of NCC at FAQ 5. </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div><div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
