          </div>
          <div id="collapse47" class="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">
            <div class="card-body">
              <p>A cadet selected as a member of the Directorate contingent, for the Republic Day Camp at Delhi, can be selected for the Republic Day Parade at Rajpath in New Delhi. </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
